{"id":220,"date":"2024-03-23T16:58:54","date_gmt":"2024-03-23T16:58:54","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/?page_id=220"},"modified":"2024-04-15T18:04:32","modified_gmt":"2024-04-15T18:04:32","slug":"stage-1ere-annee","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/stage-1ere-annee\/","title":{"rendered":"stage-1\u00e8re-ann\u00e9e"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Stage de 1\u00e8re Ann\u00e9e<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"329\" height=\"153\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_000236046.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-34\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_000236046.png 329w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_000236046-300x140.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 329px) 100vw, 329px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\"><strong>Contexte du stage&nbsp;:<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">Au cours de ma premi\u00e8re ann\u00e9e de BTS, j&rsquo;ai eu l&rsquo;opportunit\u00e9 d&rsquo;effectuer un stage au sein de la <strong>CD83, le Conseil D\u00e9partemental du Var<\/strong>. J&rsquo;ai \u00e9t\u00e9 int\u00e9gr\u00e9 au sein du service <strong>DSN, la Direction des Solutions Num\u00e9riques<\/strong>, qui constitue le service informatique du d\u00e9partement.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">Pendant une p\u00e9riode de 8 semaines, j&rsquo;ai eu l&rsquo;occasion de plonger au c\u0153ur du fonctionnement de l&rsquo;administration d\u00e9partementale du Var, de comprendre ses rouages et de m&rsquo;immerger dans le monde de l&rsquo;informatique au sein de ses locaux. Durant cette p\u00e9riode enrichissante, j&rsquo;ai eu l&rsquo;occasion de participer \u00e0 diverses missions, <strong>allant de l&rsquo;assistance de proximit\u00e9 avec les agents, d\u00e9pannages sur ordinateurs (c\u00e2blages, installations mat\u00e9rielles, installations de Switch. <\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-large-font-size\"><strong>Ma mission principale :<\/strong> <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>cr\u00e9er un plan et un rapport d\u00e9taill\u00e9 de l\u2019infrastructure r\u00e9seau qui int\u00e8gre :<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">Calcul du nombre de prises r\u00e9seaux n\u00e9cessaires au coll\u00e8ge<br>Sch\u00e9mas de distribution<br>Nomenclature des prises RJ<br>Sch\u00e9ma d\u2019implantation des cam\u00e9ras existante<br>PPMS( Plan particulier de mise en s\u00fbret\u00e9 )<br>T\u00e9l\u00e9phonie<br>Cahier des charges<br>Sch\u00e9mas des armoires et baies<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"904\" height=\"704\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-03_223748105.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-651\" style=\"width:654px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-03_223748105.png 904w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-03_223748105-300x234.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-03_223748105-768x598.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 904px) 100vw, 904px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">Ce stage m&rsquo;a permis d&rsquo;acqu\u00e9rir une exp\u00e9rience pratique pr\u00e9cieuse dans le domaine de l&rsquo;informatique au sein d&rsquo;une structure administrative d&rsquo;importance. J&rsquo;ai pu d\u00e9velopper mes comp\u00e9tences techniques, mais aussi ma capacit\u00e9 \u00e0 m&rsquo;adapter \u00e0 diff\u00e9rents environnements de travail et \u00e0 travailler en \u00e9quipe.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-1 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Synthese_de_Stage_Romain_NGUYEN_finale.docx.pdf\" style=\"border-radius:100px;background:linear-gradient(71deg,rgb(0,98,255) 0%,rgb(62,57,96) 100%);padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">Synth\u00e8se de stage<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-2 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Questionnaire-Gestion-du-Patrimoine-Bonaparte-2023.docx